REDUCE YOUR RISK OF THE CORONAVIRUS INFECTION🛑


- Clean your phones with disinfectant wipes throughout the day

- wash your hands regularly throughout the day if soap and water isn’t available use alcohol base hand sanitizer

- Wash your hands before and after eating meals

- Go out with a mask ( if reports of the virus in the area your travelling to)

- Clean your house and car

- Wipe shopping carts handles with disinfectant wipes before use

- Wipe house door knobs handles and car door handles with disinfectant wipes

- Carry dettol instant hand sanitizers

- Carry sanitation wipes

- try not to touch your face especially the eyes, nose and mouth

- Stay away from the sick

- Try to avoid public bathrooms

- Try to avoid shaking hands with people

- Try not to touch public handrails

- watch where you eat or do out business

- Try not to handle public cash.

- try to avoid theme parks, malls, Restaurants

- Try to avoid large crowds of people

- keep your children things cleaned Toys, books, school bags and shoes

- Ensure the children are not exposed near people who are showing symptoms of the cold

- teach children the importance of personal hygiene

- Eat healthy foods and drink plenty of water to boost your immune system

Stay safe and take care!!
